---
title: Lemon and Rosemary Turkey with Creamy Pasta and Broccoli
description: Long day? Too tired to cook? We know the feeling. At HelloFresh we believe that being short of time or stuck in a recipe rut shouldn’t stop you from cooking and enjoying great food. This delicious dish proves that turkey  isn’t just for Christmas. Super lean and packed with flavour, we’ve marinated our turkey steaks with lemon and rosemary to bring a zesty kick to this comforting recipe. Full on flavour in double quick time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-and-rosemary-turkey-e2ccd3eb-3744b9cf.jpg
